          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Enhancing Grid Security through Public-Private Partnerships Act </b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to facilitate and encourage public-private partnerships in order to address and mitigate the physical security and cybersecurity risks of electric utilities.</p>]]></text>
